NB. Single line comment

Note 'Multiline comment'
The verb `Note` starts a multiline comment.
')' in the next line ends this comment.
)

Note=: 'This is not a comment'

NB. Primitives
= =. =:     < <. <:     > >. >:
+ +. +:     - -. -:     * *. *:     % %. %:
^ ^. ^:     $ $. $:     ~ ~. ~:     | |. |:
. .. .:     : :. ::     , ,. ,:     ; ;. ;:
